    Exit fullscreen mode












  3. Make handlers idempotent


Webhooks can be delivered multiple times. Use upsert instead of create:



await db.subscription.upsert({
  where: { stripeSubscriptionId: sub.id },
  create: { /* ... */ },
  update: { /* ... */ },
});



